<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" type="text/css">
</head>
<body>
  <div id="background">
    <div id="page">
      {{> header}}

      <div id="contents">
        <div id="adbox">
          <img src="/images/sea-sound.jpg" alt="Beach view">
          <h1>CS 499 Capstone Portfolio</h1>
          <p>
            This portfolio presents my enhanced Travlr project as a professional showcase of software engineering, algorithms and data structures, and database design. It highlights the growth I made throughout the Computer Science program and demonstrates how I can contribute to real-world software development work.
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="/self-assessment.html" style="color:#fff; font-weight:600;">Open the professional self-assessment</a>
          </p>
        </div>

        <div id="main">
          <div class="box">
            <div>
              <div>
                <h3>Portfolio Highlights</h3>
                <ul>
                  <li>
                    <h4><a href="/code-review.html">Informal code review</a></h4>
                    <p>Review the original Travlr application and the planned enhancements that shaped the final portfolio.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <h4><a href="/artifact-software.html">Software design and engineering</a></h4>
                    <p>See how I improved the application structure, maintainability, and professional presentation.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <h4><a href="/artifact-algorithms.html">Algorithms and data structures</a></h4>
                    <p>Explore the logic behind efficient trip lookup, filtering, and data handling.</p>
                  </li>
                  <li>
                    <h4><a href="/artifact-databases.html">Databases</a></h4>
                    <p>Review the database model and API support for organized trip data management.</p>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="testimonials" class="box">
            <div>
              <div>
                <h3>Capstone Focus</h3>
                <p>
                  The artifacts in this portfolio demonstrate my ability to apply computing principles in a cohesive way, balancing user experience, technical design, and professional communication.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="sidebar">
          <div class="section">
            <a href="/rooms"><img src="/images/rooms.png" alt="Rooms"></a>
          </div>
          <div class="section">
            <a href="/dives"><img src="/images/dive-site.png" alt="Dive Sites"></a>
          </div>
          <div class="section">
            <a href="/foods"><img src="/images/food.png" alt="Dining"></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    {{> footer}}
  </div>
</body>
</html>
